What is the area of the semi-circle with center $K$?

solution:
Sketching the points, we find that the triangle is a right triangle whose legs measure $x$ and $5$ units.  Solving $\frac{1}{2}(x)(5)=30$, we find $x=\boxed{12}$.

[asy]
size(5cm,IgnoreAspect);
import graph;
defaultpen(linewidth(0.7)+fontsize(10));
real x = 12;
pair A=(0,0), B=(x,0), C=(x,5);
pair[] dots = {A,B,C};
