problem:
In the diagram, $\triangle XYZ$ is right-angled at $X,$ with $YX=60$ and $XZ=80.$ The point $W$ is on $YZ$ so that $WX$ is perpendicular to $YZ.$ Determine the length of $WZ.$ [asy]
