[/asy]

solution:
Plotting the points, we see that the dimensions of the rectangle are $x$ and $4$.  The area of the rectangle is $(\text{length})(\text{width})=4x$, so $4x=28$ and $x=\boxed{7}$. [asy]
size(5cm);
import graph;
